Come into His presence
With thanksgiving in your hearts
And give Him praise,
And give Him praise.

Come into His presence
With thanksgiving in your hearts
Your voices raise,
Your voices raise.

Give glory and honor
And power unto Him,
Jesus, the Name
Above all names.

